# Portal asset links — materialized by aeordb-lib/build.rs on every build.
# Linux/macOS: relative symlinks. Windows: NTFS junctions.
# Tracking them in git breaks Windows clones (git renders them as text
# files unless the user has core.symlinks=true + Developer Mode).
aeordb-lib/src/portal/aeor
aeordb-lib/src/portal/shared
